    "body": "If you apply the `get_blob_gasprice` function from the [EIP-4844](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/blob/master/EIPS/eip-4844.md#gas-accounting) to the `currentExcessBlobGas` value, you get `0x02` as the result, the transaction has `maxFeePerBlobGas==0x01` which is lower than the minimum value the current environment expects, therefore the transaction is invalid.",
